# Never commit archive bundles into this static-site repo.
# Avtzon.zip is a 189 MB image bundle that lives in the parent Downloads folder
# and repeatedly "sneaks into" storage/ during copy/build steps. GitHub rejects
# any file over 100 MB, so a single stray Avtzon.zip breaks the whole push.
# A published website never needs a .zip, so ignore them all as a safety net.
Avtzon.zip
*.zip

# OS / editor junk that has no place in the deploy
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini
